You are at the northern outskirts of Frostham. The city proper is to the south. A few snow covered residences are nearby. A trail leads into a valley to the north.

The last time you saw Frostham was before you entered the Monastery -- many years ago at least. Oddly, it seemed bigger and less desolate then.
