==>OBSERVATION: Frostham
You are in Frostham City, the famous winter-lover's haven. The once booming ski vacation spot seems to be a bit more run-down than in times past. The city thins out towards the north, while another section of town is to the south. To the west is a large wood structure. To the southwest is a small building. To the southeast is another small building, possibly a store.
