A nice beach with lots of tall grasses hides behind a short dune here. The Great Sea stretches out to the south. From here, you can go north, west or east. You can just glimpse some sort of tower-like structure far across the bay in the east.

You can see a small sailboat (in which is a fur sack (which is closed)) here.
