You're inside an ancient lighthouse. The place must have been deserted quite a long time ago, and is now a mess of broken stone, cobwebs and seabird droppings. The rest of the peninsula is back northwest. You can see a hole above where a stairway probably entered an upper floor of the place, but the stairway itself crumbled into dust long ago.

Your amulet suddenly gives off a bright purple flash, then returns to normal!
