==>STEP NUM: 261
==>ACT: west
==>OBSERVATION: Farm

There's a tired-looking farmer here.

The farmer sees you approach and rushes to greet you. "I saw what you did, sir, yes indeed. A mighty crazy thing to do, calling a volcano outa the water like that. But you did it! And my oyster beds thank you kindly! I'd like to repay the favor, but I'm only a poor farmer." He pauses, then searches his pockets. "Here," he says, putting something in your hand. "Found it digging in the sand. Don't know what it is, but I'll bet you can use it." He smiles and disappears into the farmhouse.

[Your score has just gone up by two points.]
